<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Moulded capital for a <rs type="objectType">base</rs> with a circular feature on top on which feet marks are visible for the statue (bronze); there is a short area of plain base below (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.87</measure>-<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.59</measure> x <measure precision="circa" dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.40</measure>   × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.83</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on four <term>fasciae</term> and one curved surface of the moulding and on the face below; both upper corners are chipped away, and the surface is damaged in many places.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02</measure>; abbreviation marks. Ligatured ΝΤ l. 4.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0300" notBefore="0101" exact="none">Second to third centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">nomenclature</rs>)</p>
</div>
