<div n="notyet" type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>The Council and the People and the Gerousia and the gold-bearing neopoioi honoured with the finest and greatest honours M. Aur. Ant. Dioskoros, son of M. Aur. Cl. T. Ant. Zenon, the son of Zenon the son of Dionysios the son of Agathopous Dioskoros [ . . .] a town councillor [ . . .</p>
</div>
<div type="commentary">
<head>Commentary</head>
<p>For the synedrion of the Chrysophoroi Neopoioi see <xref type="iAph">1044</xref> (=MAMA 523), <xref type="iAph">1046</xref> (=MAMA 525) (where again they are linked with Council and Gerousia), <xref type="iAph">1484</xref>  (=MAMA 555),   <xref type="iAph">1566</xref> (=MAMA 579), <xref type="iAph">1467</xref> (= CIG 2836b)</p>
</div>
